
RSS to twitter

* rsstotwitter is a very simple tool to update twitter
accounts from RSS feeds. It is written in python and
licensed under GPL

* Author: Luis Cañas Díaz <lcanasdiaz@gmail.com>

* rsstotwitter.py default.cfg

* example of configuration file.
(the fourth parameter is optional)

[Configuration]
username=your_twitter_user
password=your_twitter_password
feed_url=http://libresoft.es/ourplanet/daily-planet/RSS
include_title=Some text before the entry content here

* need help?: 

rsstotwitter.py --help

* dependencies

python-twitter
